49:21.120 --> 49:23.840
Moon! That's despicable.
You don't like it?

49:23.840 --> 49:25.160
I love it. Yeah, yeah.

49:26.160 --> 49:30.120
Reno, we should have teamed up
years ago.

49:31.560 --> 49:35.640
We're two of a kind, all right.
Partners.

49:35.640 --> 49:37.560
Through thick or thin.

